## Best Practices

### Accessibility (WCAG AA)
- Skip-to-content link
- Viewport: `user-scalable=yes, maximum-scale=5.0`
- 44px min touch target (mobile)
- ARIA labels on navigation (`aria-label`, `aria-current`)
- Semantic HTML (`<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`)
- Motion preferences respected (`prefers-reduced-motion`)
- Proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)
- Descriptive alt text for images
- Keyboard navigation support

### SEO
- Unique titles: "[Page Name] - DBCA Global"
- Meta descriptions: 150-160 characters
- Canonical URLs on all pages
- Open Graph + Twitter card tags (all pages)
- Structured data (Organization schema on homepage)
- Semantic HTML structure

### Performance
- Parallax uses `requestAnimationFrame` for smooth performance
- Passive event listeners for scroll events
- Images optimized (WebP where possible)
- Google Fonts with `display=swap`
- Conditional Google Analytics (production only)
- No JavaScript frameworks (vanilla JS only)

### JavaScript Features
- Parallax scrolling (respects reduced motion)
- Mobile navigation toggle
- Smooth scroll for anchor links
- Scroll-triggered animations (Intersection Observer)
- Navbar scroll effect (transparent → white)

